The paper focuses on content-based detection of fake news articles, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques (cs.CL, cs.IR). The use of tensor decomposition and embeddings also suggests a machine learning and data mining approach (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of limited labels and a semi-supervised setting, which are common themes in artificial intelligence research (cs.AI).
